summary: This document appears to be a certification from the Lieutenant Governor of the Virgin Islands regarding the filing of Articles of Incorporation for a corporation. It includes a declaration of the persons named in the Articles and their rights of succession.
locations: Charlotte Amalie, St. Thomas, Virgin Islands
keyFacts: The document certifies the filing of Articles of Incorporation on August 18, 2003.
It is issued by the Lieutenant Governor of the Virgin Islands.
The document is marked as confidential.
